textBeforeTable: Acknowledged on October 28, 2014 & January 27, 2015 In an ongoing feature, the Board wishes to pay tribute to those who have been registered California pharmacists on active status for at least 50 years. The Board of Pharmacy recognizes these individuals and gratefully acknowledges their years of contribution to the pharmacy profession. These pharmacists may take great pride in being part of such an honorable profession for so long. 50-Year Pharmacists Fax (916) 574-8618 Phone (916) 574-7900 Sacramento, CA 95834 Contact Us 1625 N Market Blvd, N219 What's New Medicare Part D Info Newsletter - The Script Contact Us Enforcement Actions Board
